//- Variables for includes
basePath = "/vgm-service-line-up"
pageTitle = "Service Line Up"

doctype 5
html(lang='en')
  include _head
  body
    include _header
    section.guide-main.container
      section.hero.guide-section.cf
        .hero-image
          .image
        h2.hero-subtitle Take the pain out of managing your business
        p.hero-text You need to spend your time where it matters most&mdash;growing your business
        a.btn-primary.icon-right Learn more
      section.guide-section.tagline-section
        h2.tagline Let Service Line Up worry about the details:
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-calendar 
        h3.point-title Scheduling
        p Easily do scheduling with our smart scheduler. See what days and times you have available and schedule customers quickly and easily. Once you schedule a customer on a recurring appointment the system will generate their appointment automatically so you know what your schedule looks like weeks in advance.
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-coin 
        h3.point-title Billing
        p Get paid with the click of a button through Service Line Up. By signing up with our preferred merchant you gain the ability to do all your credit card processing directly through our system. Easily keep track of payments in one simple place. With the ability to sort by unpaid, Credit Cards, or Checks only, getting paid couldn&rsquo;t be easier.
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-users 
        h3.point-title Customers
        p Keep track of all your customers with the ability to make notes, store pertinent information about the customer and their appointments. Your customers do not have to worry about their information because it is completely secure using 128 bit SSL security.
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-briefcase 
        h3.point-title Contractors
        p All of your contractors will be easy to keep track of with Service Line Up. Knowing when they get paid and how they get paid is all in one place.
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-stats 
        h3.point-title Reports
        p From Payroll to Appointment Reports, Service Line Up has it all. The reports are designed to give you as much information as possible. They have been field tested so we know what information you will need to get your contractors to their job on time with all the information they will need.
      section.guide-section.home-point
        i.point-icon.icon-lock 
        h3.point-title Security
        p Service Line Up was built with highest possible security in mind. Not only do we use 128 bit AES key SSL security throughout the site, we also use a secure up to date Microsoft SQL 2012 database with enhanced form protection against SQL injections and buffer overruns.
      section.guide-section.home-cta
        a.btn-primary.icon-cart(href="#{basePath}/products") Buy Now
    include _footer